{"tid":817592,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今日個00後話好期待山竹打到黎 可以放假  我即刻屌佢老母","createTime":"2018-09-13T12:52:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T15:17:49.000Z","uid":1734,"like":22,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f876f4dfd76734b41956b9b0f594a51e5bd575b6","tid":817592,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:52:50.000Z","msg":"今日成班同事食飯係到討論緊個山竹台風，80後90後開始擔心個風會對香港有危險，希望佢吹走，點知個00後竟然話好想打風，可以星期日唔洗返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我即刻拍台屌佢老母  大聲到隔離台都呆左  佢個樣即刻震撚曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我話呢個時候仲諗住放假？ 你傻撚左呀 之後成班同事讚好話我好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  班女仲話估唔到我係咁正經正氣 仲約我今晚食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實講真我都想打風放假 不過借屌個00後可以比女圍 真係好 個00後抵死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  班女彩都唔再彩佢"},{"pid":"acd83e3a1a36a9613003f09e9f6940e9ed587660","tid":817592,"uid":810,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:53:38.000Z","msg":"唔係話針對００後<br />\n但事實００後真係比較弱智。。。"},{"pid":"875e70cdbb266101c89f79df92120b90630f65f2","tid":817592,"uid":1734,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acd83e3a1a36a9613003f09e9f6940e9ed587660","tid":817592,"uid":810,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:53:38.000Z","msg":"唔係話針對００後<br />\n但事實００後真係比較弱智。。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:54:21.000Z","msg":"系 多數00後都係唔用腦 同80 90 後差好遠"},{"pid":"b6a0613eda91e23d3f973bc529f0f3a172aec4a7","tid":817592,"uid":106426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:57:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"daaad97a50939efbe8173ba166b3311f8644952b","tid":817592,"uid":209692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T13:03:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a97527fe69233c3cfcbd8ef4da116a3